    "cwc_faqs_YWQeVA": {
      "type": "CWC_faqs",
      "blocks": {
        "faq_ATbdcF": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<p><strong>WHY OLLIE?<\/strong><\/p>",
            "text": "<p>Ollie uses <strong>dentist-recommended hydroxyapatite<\/strong>—a breakthrough mineral that helps strengthen enamel, reduce sensitivity, and naturally brighten your smile without the burn.<\/p><p>Every brush delivers:<\/p><ul><li><strong>Gentle whitening<\/strong> without peroxide<\/li><li><strong>Enamel support<\/strong> with nano-hydroxyapatite<\/li><li><strong>Cleaner ingredients<\/strong> (no SLS, no parabens, no artificial dyes)<\/li><li><strong>A fresh mint taste<\/strong> that actually lasts<br\/><\/li><\/ul><p>Ollie makes daily brushing feel good, work better, and protect your smile long-term.<\/p><p><\/p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_yfNy6G": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<p><strong>SCIENCE & QUALITY?<\/strong><\/p>",
            "text": "<p>Ollie is built around ingredients backed by modern oral-care science.<\/p><p><strong>Hydroxyapatite Technology:<br\/><\/strong>Hydroxyapatite is the primary mineral found in human enamel. Research shows that nHAp can help smooth the enamel surface, support remineralization, and improve tooth comfort—without the irritation associated with peroxide or SLS.<\/p><p><strong>Gentle Whitening:<br\/><\/strong>Instead of bleaching, Ollie uses surface-polishing minerals that help remove stains from coffee, tea, and everyday life—leaving teeth looking cleaner and brighter over time.<\/p><p><strong>Safe for Daily Use<\/strong><\/p><p>Our formula is:<\/p><ul><li>Dentist-recommended<\/li><li>Fluoride-free<\/li><li>SLS-free<\/li><li>Non-toxic<\/li><li>Made in high-quality manufacturing facilities with strict standards<br\/><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Quality You Can Trust:<br\/><\/strong>Every batch is tested to ensure consistency, safety, and purity. We use only premium-grade ingredients so you get the same exceptional experience every time you brush.<\/p><p><\/p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_99Mej4": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<p><strong>INGREDIENTS & BENEFITS?<\/strong><\/p>",
            "text": "<p>Ollie Clean Mint Toothpaste is powered by a blend of safe, effective ingredients designed to support a healthier, brighter smile:<\/p><p><strong>Nano-Hydroxyapatite (nHAp): <\/strong>A mineral that mimics the natural structure of your enamel. Helps smooth the tooth surface, reduce sensitivity, and support a naturally whiter look.<\/p><p><strong>Xylitol:<\/strong><br\/>Helps support a healthy oral environment and discourage harmful bacteria.<\/p><p><strong>Aloe Vera Extract:<br\/><\/strong>Soothes gums and promotes a comfortable brushing experience—especially for those with sensitivity or irritation.<\/p><p><strong>Mint Extracts: <\/strong>Provides long-lasting freshness without artificial flavors.<\/p><p><strong>Clean-Ingredient Formula:<br\/><\/strong>No SLS, no artificial dyes, no parabens, no fluoride, and no unnecessary filler ingredients. Just what your mouth needs—and nothing it doesn’t.<\/p><p><strong>Benefits at a glance:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Helps strengthen enamel<\/li><li>Brightens teeth naturally<\/li><li>Reduces day-to-day sensitivity<\/li><li>Freshens breath<\/li><li>Supports long-term oral health<\/li><li>Safe for daily use, even for sensitive teeth<\/li><\/ul><p><\/p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_VFh4g3": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<p><strong>HOW LONG UNTIL I SEE RESULTS?<\/strong><\/p>",
            "text": "<p>Many customers notice smoother, cleaner-feeling teeth after the first few uses. Brightening benefits are typically seen within<strong>1–2 weeks<\/strong>of consistent use.<\/p><p><\/p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_jEV6Vm": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<p><strong>DOES IT WHITEN TEETH?<\/strong><\/p>",
            "text": "<p>Yes! Ollie helps brighten teeth by gently reducing surface stains and supporting a smoother enamel surface. There’s no peroxide, so whitening happens gradually and comfortably.<\/p><p><\/p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_p7UgXt": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<p><strong>IS IT SAFE FOR SENSITIVE TEETH?<\/strong><\/p>",
            "text": "<p>Absolutely. The formula was made specifically for sensitive mouths. Hydroxyapatite helps calm sensitivity while strengthening enamel, making brushing more comfortable over time.<\/p><p><\/p>"
          }
        },
